snippet.title: The British Takeaway Awards 2017: Driver of the Year  - Chris McKeating
snippet.description:
Chris Mckeating, of The Chef's Table is rewarded for his decidation, determination and love for delivering food to your door. We secretly filmed him to see how he'd react to the news.

The British Takeaway Awards 2017 were hosted by John Bishop at The Savoy London.



Have a look at our other videos: http://www.youtube.com/user/TVjusteat

Order takeaway: http://www.JUST-EAT.co.uk
